snippet.title: Best VGM 2414 - Harvest Moon : Magical Melody - Fall Theme
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

GameCube / Wii
Harvest Moon: Magical Melody (2005)
Fall Theme
Miyuki Homareda
